cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.CV, cs.AI 

The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks for classification of textual data, which falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on incremental learning and discovering new classes of data also suggests a strong connection to the machine learning and artificial intelligence sub-fields.
